Libraries required:
- cv2
- torch
- numpy
- serial
- time
- torchvision
- ultralytics

GPU Requirements:
To run this project on GPU, ensure you have an NVIDIA GPU with compatible drivers and have installed the CUDA Toolkit 12.6.
Install the correct PyTorch and torchvision versions with CUDA 12.6 support:

pip install torch==2.6.0+cu126 torchvision==0.21.0+cu126 --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cu126

You can download the appropriate CUDA Toolkit 12.6 from:
https://developer.nvidia.com/cuda-downloads
